name: Ebru #5
description: Single edition abstract digital painting. The Ebru series is inspired by Ebru (paper marbling) technique which was originated in East Asia and used extensively in Turkey, Middle East and to a smaller extend in Europe. The “Ebru” series aims to build a bridge between traditional and digital techniques. Series consist of 9 single edition OBJKTs and one free OBJKT with 200 editions. All images in this series are 4000x5000 pixels.
